or slams, and the row of hotels means plenty of people coming home late and chatting. But after a bit I fell asleep and wasn't bothered.My only real complaint is that the two pillows were too flat by themselves and too high and stiff together. And a mattress pad with some give would be nice for those of us who *don't* want a rock hard bed. But at least it wasn't lumpy.	
